,'<p>Dienstag und Mittwoch, 11.00 &ndash; 13.30 Uhr und 14.00 &ndash; 19.00 Uhr<br />Donnerstag und Freitag, 11.00 &ndash; 13.30 Uhr und 14.00 &ndash; 20.00 Uhr<br />Samstag, 10.00 &ndash; 17.00 Uhr</p><p>oder nach Vereinbarung</p>','<p>Tuesday &amp; Wednesday, 11am ‒ 1.30pm &amp; 2 ‒7pm<br />Thursday &amp; Friday, 11am ‒ 1.30pm &amp; 2 ‒ 8pm<br />Saturday, 10am ‒ 5pm</p><p>or by prior arrangement</p>','<p>Mardi et mercredi, 11h &ndash; 13h30 et 14h &ndash; 19h<br />Jeudi et vendredi, 11h &ndash; 13h30 et 14h &ndash; 20h<br />Samedi, 10h &ndash; 17h</p><p>ou sur rendez-vous</p>','<p>Martedì e mercoledì, 11.00 &ndash; 13.30 e 14.00 &ndash; 19.00<br />Giovedì e venerdì, 11.00 &ndash; 13.30 e 14.00 &ndash; 20.00<br />Sabato, 10.00 &ndash; 17.00</p><p>o su appuntamento</p>','Tuesday,Wednesday,Thursday,Friday,Saturday','POINT (47.375193 8.5401452)',1,'https://cdn.zuerich.com/sites/default/files/web_zuerich_placart_1280x960_27053.jpg',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),
